Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Taren, I'm Commander Jenny.\NI'm here to make a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've felt this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the stars clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Mariko O'Brien captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize. We're still searching for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we've obtained information\Nthat she escaped into the old city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, we'll be able to arrest her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has come, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try using Caligula.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Caligula? The class-A war criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people should be able to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that, Commander Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Major! In fifteen minutes, we'll arrive at the\Nsite of a small scale battle, Area JF5025.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So should we finish this quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your breath smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this included a shoulder massage service!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I was getting tired of those handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try anything funny, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one way a class-A war\Ncriminal like you can stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, get ready for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the area under control ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the female target there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely. This time, we won't let her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an old friend working at a junk store in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let him guide us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to land in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the target area is still far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye, you incompetent failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sensor is picking it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The woman who single-handedly took\Non a hundred-year battle with Gatt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For a person who's preparing to die,\Nyou seem quite relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because I'm with you, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I the compensation for risking your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.84,0:24:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.64,0:24:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.23,0:24:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The robot continues to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}towards an eventual end,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.23,0:24:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with only one goal, just one goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It never tires or considers the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.74,0:24:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The flames from the burning wreckage\Nwill one day fill the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.74,0:24:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cities will disappear into the seabed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acid rain will rot everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.32,0:25:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than the blood of the fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.00,0:25:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the storm of scrap metal wards them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tims drags on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.51,0:25:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The robot continues to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.64,0:25:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with only one goal, just one goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}forgetting even what it means to be tired.